		<description><![CDATA[Fascinating photography that’s covered subjects both large and small]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="1600" height="1067" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/ArchivalIssue_2023_Roundup_1800_02_Visual.jpg" class="webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image" alt="A blue background with text that says Our Best Visual Essays" loading="lazy" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; clear:both;max-width: 100%;" link_thumbnail="" srcset="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/ArchivalIssue_2023_Roundup_1800_02_Visual.jpg 1600w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/ArchivalIssue_2023_Roundup_1800_02_Visual-735x490.jpg 735w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/ArchivalIssue_2023_Roundup_1800_02_Visual-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/ArchivalIssue_2023_Roundup_1800_02_Visual-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/ArchivalIssue_2023_Roundup_1800_02_Visual-348x232.jpg 348w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><div style="max-width: 1500px;" class="special-series-body beauty-series">
