<h6>BY LOUISE BERNICE HALFE</h6>
<h5 style="font-family: GT Sectra; font-weight: 200;">Real life on the rez</h5>
</div></div>
</div>
<STORY END></p>
<hr class="thin">
<STORY START><br />
<div class="su-row"><div class="su-column su-column-size-2-5"><div class="su-column-inner su-u-clearfix su-u-trim">
<a href="https://thewalrus.ca/if-these-walls-could-talk/"><img loading="lazy" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/12-7-IfTheseWallsCouldTalk1.jpg" alt="" width="735" height="490" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-110841" /></a><br />
</div></div>
